  "texts": [
    "For example, P1 reported, \"I didn't feel like I did anything, so it kind of feels like cheating. \"",
    "P8 even directly expressed the desire to receive more engaging help, as \"\"there could be something like more engaging than just reading the code. \"",
    "6.2.2 RQ2: Students applied more supported elements on the posttest when using CodeTailor as practice support than when receiving an AI-generated solution.",
    "All the students got a full score (20 of 20) in the practice when using the baseline support.",
    "This was expected, as they could just copy the correct solution and submit it."
  ]
